name: BetterBurnTime
desc: Accurate burn time indicator on navball. No more "N/A"! Compensates for fuel consumption. Includes time-to-impact and closest-approach tracker.
author: Snark

name: BetterCrewAssignment
desc: Smarter by default. Remembers your choices. No UI.
author: Snark

name: Chatterer
desc: A plugin for Kerbal Space Program which adds some SSTV, beeps, and nonsensical radio chatter between your command pods and Mission Control.
author: Athlonic

name: CommunityResourcePack
desc: Common resources for KSP mods
author: RoverDude

name: CommunityTechTree
desc: An extension for the stock technology tree designed to support many mods
author: Nertea

name: ConnectedLivingSpace
desc: This mod identifies areas within a vessel that can be crewed by Kerbals and through which kerbals can pass internally to reach other parts that can be crewed.
author: Papa_Joe

name: ContractConfigurator
desc: A config-file based solution for creating new contracts!
author: nightingale

name: ContractParser
desc: Parse the contract module to cache data
author: DMagic1

name: ContractsWindowPlus
desc: A new, more flexible contract monitoring window.
author: DMagic

name: CrowdSourcedFlags
desc: A collection of community-created flags, including Kerbal flags, Earth countries and more. If you have a flag of your own that you want to add, please do! Use a pull request to the repo or make a post in the subreddit (/r/KSP_CrowdSourcedFlags).
author: GenericAerospace

name: DarkMultiPlayer
desc: DMP is a multiplayer mod for kerbal space program.
author: godarklight

name: DistantObject
desc: Visual enhancement mod that makes objects realistically visible over large distances.
author: MOARdV

name: DistantObject-default
desc: Default planets colors
author: MOARdV

name: DMagicOrbitalScience
desc: New science parts and experiments
author: DMagic

name: FerramAerospaceResearch
desc: FAR replaces KSP's stock part-centered aerodynamics model with one based on real-life physics.
author: ferram4

name: FirespitterCore
desc: Core Firespitter.dll. Install `Firespitter` for the whole shebang
author: Roverdude

name: InterstellarFuelSwitch
desc: Library that enables switching the contents, meshes, and textures of tanks.
author: FreeThinker

name: InterstellarFuelSwitch-Core
desc: Core plugin for Interstellar Fuel Switch
author: FreeThinker

name: Karbonite
desc: A newly discovered mineral that has hydrocarbon-like properties and is perfect for processing into a fuel. It's easily mined from the surface, and can be found in liquid or gaseous forms on certain planets.
author: RoverDude

name: KarbonitePlus
desc: New resources and parts for Karbonite, including the resource Karborundum
author: RoverDude

name: KAS
desc: KAS introduces new gameplay mechanics by adding winches, containers, dynamic struts/pipes and grabbable & attachable parts.
author: KospY

name: KerbalEngineerRedux
desc: Reveals important statistics about your ship and its orbit during building and flight
author: CYBUTEK

name: Kerbalism
desc: Add life support, quality-of-life, radiation, malfunctions, signals and space weather mechanics.
author: ShotgunNinja

name: KerbalJointReinforcement
desc: KJR tightens up the joints between parts and adds some physics-adjusting parameters to make vehicles more stable when loading on the launchpad or coming out of timewarp.
author: ferram4

name: KerbodynePlus
desc: An end-game parts pack.
author: BonusEventus

name: KIS
desc: KIS introduces new gameplay mechanics by adding a brand new inventory system and EVA usables items as tools. You want to build a rover on Duna from scratch? Now you can...
author: KospY

name: Kopernicus
desc: Allows users to replace the planetary system used by the game.
author: BryceSchroeder

name: kOS
desc: kOS is a scriptable autopilot Mod for Kerbal Space Program. It allows you write small programs that automate specific tasks.
author: erendrake

name: KronalVesselViewer
desc: Plugin that creates blue-print-like images (into your <KSP Root>Screenshots/ directory) from the KSP Editor (VAB/SPH).
author: bigorangemachine

name: KSPInterstellarExtended
desc: KSP Interstellar Extended is a plugin for Kerbal Space Program, designed to encourage bootstrapping toward ever more advanced levels of technology as well as utilizing In-Situ resources to expand the reach of Kerbal civilization. KSP Interstellar Extended aims to continue in Fractals original KSPI vision in providing a realistic road to the stars.
author: FreeThinker

name: KWRocketryRedux
desc: This is the full KW Rocketry with the Community Fixes included.  Repackaged so that the power configs are selecteable in CKAN
author: linuxgurugamer

name: KWRocketryRedux-GraduatedPwr
desc: For graduated power response on engines
author: linuxgurugamer

name: MainSailorTextures-Complete
desc: Procedural Parts textures by MainSailor - Includes Gamma, Historical, Theta and Fairings packs
author: MainSailor

name: ModuleManager
desc: Modify KSP configs without conflict
author: ialdabaoth

name: PlanetShine
desc: Planets and moons reflects their light to your vessel + other ambient light improvements
author: Valerian

name: PlanetShine-Config-Default
desc: Planets and moons reflects their light to your vessel + other ambient light improvements
author: Valerian

name: ProceduralFairings
desc: Fairings that automatically reshape for any attached payload
author: e-dog

name: ProceduralParts
desc: ProceduralParts allows you to procedurally generate a number of different parts in a range of sizes and shapes.
author: ItMustBeACamel

name: ProgressParser
desc: Parse the progress tree for completion rewards
author: DMagic1

name: RasterPropMonitor
desc: RasterPropMonitor is a plugin and toolkit that provides functional props within your IVA.
author: MOARdV

name: RasterPropMonitor-Core
desc: RasterPropMonitor is a plugin and toolkit that provides functional props within your IVA.
author: MOARdV

name: RealChute
desc: RealChute is a complete rework of the stock parachute module to fix a few of it's inconveniences and get more realistic results out of parachutes!
author: stupid_chris

name: RealPlume
desc: A set of effects and basic configs that can be attached to any engine as appropriate.  Requires secondary configs to function correctly.
author: Felger

name: RealPlume-StockConfigs
desc: A set of effects and basic configs that can be attached to any engine as appropriate.  Requires secondary configs to function correctly.
author: Nhawks1717

name: RemoteTech
desc: Community developed continuation of Kerbal Space Program's RemoteTech mod.
author: Remote Technologies Group

name: SCANsat
desc: SCANsat: Real Scanning, Real Science, Warp Speed!
author: DMagic

name: Scatterer
desc: Atmospheric scattering shaders
author: blackrack

name: ShipManifest
desc: Ship Manifest is a tool to manage your ship's "things".
author: Papa_Joe

name: SmokeScreen
desc: SmokeScreen is a plugin that build on the engine FX added in .23 and adds new features to them. Most of the features ideas comes from Nothke.
author: Sarbian

name: TweakScale
desc: TweakScale lets you change the size of a part. Not just that, but it will figure out how much fuel is in the resized part. And if it's an engine, it will become more powerful by scaling it bigger, or weaker by scaling it smaller.
author: Biotronic

name: UniversalStorage
desc: Modular parts pack for creating Apollo style service modules, compatible with many life support mods and KAS/KIS
author: Paul_Kingtiger

name: WaypointManager
desc: Display waypoints while in flight, create custom waypoints.
author: nightingale

name: FilterExtensions
desc: Plugin allowing for configurable filters for the VAB/SPH using .cfg files.
author: Crzyrndm

name: Toolbar
desc: API for third-party plugins to provide toolbar buttons
author: blizzy78

name: CapCom
desc: A contract management window available in all scenes; accept, decline, or cancel contracts without going back to the Mission Control Center
author: DMagic

name: ContractRewardModifier
desc: An in-game utility for customizing all contract and parameter rewards and penalties, among other options.
author: DMagic

name: ModularFlightIntegrator
